                </h3>
                <p class="style="color: var(--text-tertiary);" leading-relaxed">
                    The entire system was orchestrated using ROS (Robot Operating System). Custom nodes were developed to subscribe to YOLOv5 perception topics, process the 3D coordinates, send goals to the MoveIt! planner, and execute the planned trajectory on the physical UR3e robotic arm.
